      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait sorry, what do you mean by \"goblin parade\" and \"shaman\"? i'm just trying to fix my model, i don't really get the metaphors. can you just stick to the math? also, what kind of robust regression would you suggest specifically for outliers?",
